{"tid":637753,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"喜訊: 香港著名性感女星招親","createTime":"2018-04-22T06:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T10:22:49.000Z","uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f179c765da55857121e2ab031724eb4d4a136d","tid":637753,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"欣宜入行時受盡批評，她有感而發讀出草蜢金曲《失樂園》歌詞「結果我共你，仍然逃不過被圍攻、被捨棄」來形容當時心情，「我成日俾人批評，但無放棄自己，就算我知自己是負分，都想盡努力由負分變零分，再一分一分加上去，我深信只要堅持努力，總有一日會合格，希望大家看完今晚演唱會，畀一個公道的分數我。」成功實現紅館夢，她不禁興奮地笑道：「相信只有夢想堅持可成真，我的紅館夢想成真了！<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>要計劃第二個夢想，搵返個Dream Guy結婚生仔</strong></span>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊位烈士有興趣"},{"pid":"9dfa039e6303aa7e8194188e5fb2470494450198","tid":637753,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29507be3eb27605a0abe0ed6980a8ef4d0a1b529","tid":637753,"uid":151926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:28:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快</span>"},{"pid":"a802afeb4260559759f2eff680eb93396b9fa226","tid":637753,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:29:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不如我地...</span></span>"},{"pid":"6d61cc29806aedbd098d488522f3dbaa9a7ef315","tid":637753,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a802afeb4260559759f2eff680eb93396b9fa226","tid":637753,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:29:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不如我地...</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T06:35:26.000Z","msg":"淨係同你做就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d982d18efe98b35